- **Decisions:** No brand assets exist for KS Global Estates; invent identity. Palette: charcoal `#12100E` / parchment `#F5F1EB` / muted gold `#B8975A`. Type: Cormorant Garamond (display) + DM Sans (body). Leaflet 1.9.4 + CARTO Voyager tile confirmed. Frontend-only (no Flask blueprint). Mock DB = JS module.
